https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/agPWHv5r5jkfdoVGgFVzpbehIQ1.jpg Star student Jade and her mother Frida, a crime author, have a great relationship. But when she discovers Frida’s secret financial problems, Jade joins her bad-boy crush Rick in a series of high-profile burglaries that net enough cash to pay off Frida’s debts. However when she tries to quit the criminal world, Rick’s gang have other ideas – and now both Jade and Frida must fight for their very lives. Deadly Secrets
